Along with the rest of the Tennessee Congressional Delegation, I urged President @realDonaldTrump to quickly approve @GovBillLee’s request for additional federal assistance for the state of Tennessee to assist with the COVID-19 pandemic. 

https://t.co/T9juN4B04E https://t.co/4wyNMWicfN

full_text: Thank you to all the doctors on the front lines who are delivering lifesaving care during the #COVID19 crisis. full_text: Today marks the 100th anniversary of the women’s right to vote. Did you know TN played a pivotal role in ratifying the 19th Amendment? It was the 36th & final state to sign it into law. As we celebrate this historic milestone let’s remember all those who helped make it a reality. https://t.co/Yv6Kpu6CaH

full_text: Last week, I signed on to HR 714, the EL CHAPO Act. It seeks to fund border security and a border wall by using billions of dollars in seized drug money profits from drug cartels. This is a common sense approach to increase funding for border security and I'm happy to support it.
